{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-05157/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-05157"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:51:57"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man scratches his head as a woman gazes to people offscreen."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05157/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-05157","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05157/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-05157"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05157/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05157/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05157/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05157/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05157/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05157/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05157/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05157/canvas/1/31264291-c3e5-4fba-b795-bcf93f8f328e","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T20:05:39.852Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds, clearly uncomfortable, turns away from the scene, casting his eyes downward and awkwardly scratching his head. He seemingly cannot bear the intensity of the press conference. In contrast, Alma stares straight ahead of her, despite her visible distress. She, unlike Reynolds, is unafraid to face what makes her uncomfortable, calling back to her <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW76949142 BCX0\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-02158.html\"><u>earlier promise</u></a> that if he will lose any staring contest he starts with her.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05157/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:644.0583456425464,110.03646602658793,998.3059453471193,460.01200147710483"}}}]}]}]}